text: Vladimir Romanishin (born 27 August 1959) is a Soviet rower. He competed at the 1988 Summer Olympics and the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1959 births Category:Living people Category:Soviet male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of the Soviet Union Category:Olympic rowers of the Unified Team Category:Rowers at the 1988 Summer Olympics Category:Rowers at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
